113
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,759
Dongfang Xi getting close
to her brother.

114
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,759
If only I'd noticed sooner…

115
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:38,160
Dongfang Zhan, please be safe.

116
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,079
A woman's reputation is more fragile
than anything.

117
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:44,959
It's so easy to destroy.

118
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:51,839
No matter how powerful her family is,

119
