122
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,399
You're playing with fire!

123
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,079
I…

124
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,759
I'm going to post that video right now!

125
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,920
I'll ruin Dongfang Xi!

126
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:39,080
Shoot! It's a dead end.

